    "How is GPT's (considerable and surprising) performance capacity limited by the fact that all of GPT's content-words lack T3 sensorimotor grounding?",
    "GPT would be incapable of recognizing or interacting with the referents of those words in the physical world, even though GPT can describe and discuss them verbally.",
